The paper deals with the problem of repairing databases under integrity constraints, which is a core topic in the field of databases (cs.DB). The use of aggregation constraints and the study of consistency of answers to aggregate conjunctive queries suggest a connection to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The investigation of complexity and approximation algorithms is a common theme in theoretical computer science (cs.CC) and algorithm design (cs.DS).
